The paper discusses the impact of quantum computers on cryptography, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). It also discusses the need for software engineers to prepare for the era of quantum advantage, which involves software development (cs.SE) and programming languages (cs.PL). Additionally, the paper touches on the storage and processing of data, which could fall under the categories of information theory (cs.IT) and cybernetics (cs.CY).
